<h1>About This Project</h1>

<p>
  Dog Breed Explorer is a Ruby on Rails application built using the AKC Dog Breed CSV dataset.
  The dataset includes information about dog breed names, descriptions, popularity,
  height, weight, life expectancy, grooming, shedding, energy level, trainability,
  demeanor, group, and temperament.
</p>

<h2>Data Sources</h2>

<ul>
  <li>AKC Dog Breed CSV dataset</li>
  <li>Sample review data created inside the Rails seed file</li>
</ul>

<h2>Database Design</h2>

<p>
  The application uses five models: Breed, Group, Temperament, BreedTemperament, and Review.
</p>

